"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-02-parisolympics-jamaicas-kirlew-elated-olympics-debut-100m-butterfly\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"History was rewritten Friday at La Defense Arena in western Paris when swimmer Josh Kirlew became the first Jamaican in 40 years to feature in the men's Olympic 100m butterfly.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 60, \"end\": 65, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9995147755497925, \"rank\": 0.00048546000718833907, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 79, \"end\": 83, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.8423792212722335, \"rank\": 0.18704860850886193, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 108, \"end\": 116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9968412917599018, \"rank\": 0.0031687000660954325, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"History\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 7}, {\"ngram\": \"La Defense Arena\", \"from\": 32, \"to\": 48}, {\"ngram\": \"40 years\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24 year-old London-based athlete emerged from the pool without his hoped new personal best, but with a beaming smile on his face after finishing fifth in an opening heat of five, designed for athletes eligible through the 'Universality' system, where emerging nations are allowed one male and one female representative, irrespective of the stringent qualifying times.\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 24 year-old London-based athlete\", \"from\"